snippet: Derek Fathauer played bogey-free for a six-under-par 66, building a one-shot lead over Jason Bohn going into the final round of the O.H.L. Classic in Playa del Carmen, Mexico.
abstract: Derek Fathauer takes third round lead at OHL Classic golf tournament; other golf news noted.
